This vims-script create your all plugin's helptags.

How to use:

<in Ex-mode>
:HelpDocLoad('~/.vim/bundle')

<in .vimrc>
HelpDocLoad('~/.vim/bundle')

=====

** FAQ **

Q. My vim can't find existing language help doc! 
(I have english doc. But my vim tries to find japanese doc only.)

A. Use this option in vimrc/ex-mode.
set helplang=en,ja

